  "title": "ReFi Roundup #41: COP27 & Optimism in ReFi",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-41",
  "html": "<p>Hello ReFi frens, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/linggih_ngurah?t=tG04Tv0kmB78ym39ANaBpQ&amp;s=09\">Nura</a> here with the latest ReFi Roundup. I am working on <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ngurah-nura-linggih-b1877742/\">sustainability tech solutions</a> during the day, and a Climate x Web3 writer @<a href=\"https://enjoytheweather.substack.com/\">EnjoytheWeather</a> at night. Â Let's find out what's gold in the ReFi world this week!</p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/11/image-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"329\" height=\"173\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://cop27.eg/\">www.cop27.eg</a></figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"cop27putting-refi-on-the-map-%F0%9F%97%BA%EF%B8%8F\">COP27 - Putting ReFi on the map! ğŸ—ºï¸</h2><p>COP27 is happening this week in Egypt. Climate change is a global coordination problem and COP can be a place to explore systems of coordination and build bridges. It's also the first time ReFi is making it's presence known as part of the solution. Let's dive in to the thinking behind this, what is going down, and which countries are leading the way...</p><h3 id=\"making-the-case-%F0%9F%92%BC\">Making the case! ğŸ’¼</h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/_newcubes_\">@_newcubes</a> recently wrote an amazing article for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RegenFdn\">Regen Foundation</a> \"Community Stake in the New Regenerative Economy â†’ Towards COP27\". </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://regenfoundation.mirror.xyz/sYFgtGQmSrfx-L8hxR8eaZJo6bpcjviE4haxgjALvBo\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">The Regenerative Revolution will be Community Owned and Governed</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Without being structural shift in resource flow to regenerators, the long term benefits of carbon markets and climate finance is hurting more than helping.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://regenfoundation.mirror.xyz/icon/favicon-32x32.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://mirror-media.imgix.net/publication-images/UUwknYVWbEtooXqqmpoVR.jpeg?height&#x3D;414&amp;width&#x3D;828&amp;h&#x3D;414&amp;w&#x3D;828&amp;auto&#x3D;compress\" alt=\"\"></div></a><figcaption>Thanks to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThoughtFloats\">@ThoughtFloats</a> for sharing this article!</figcaption></figure><p>It explores <a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/news/feature/2022/05/17/what-you-need-to-know-about-article-6-of-the-paris-agreement\">Article 6 of the Paris agreement</a> which governs the rule of international carbon markets and was signed in COP26 last year. But what's holding it back? and what is the way forward? ğŸ‘‡ </p><h4 id=\"problem-statements\">Problem statements:</h4><p>ğŸ”¬ <strong>Integrity of science and data</strong>. It's hard to validate data behind claims of regeneration. Lack of transparency and accountability in the assurance process.</p><p>ğŸ—£ï¸ <strong>Political process:</strong> Decisions are made behind closed doors. Local communities are not involved in deciding the future of their own ecosystem </p><h4 id=\"proposed-solutions\">Proposed solutions:</h4><p>ğŸ‘ï¸ <strong>Freed from carbon tunnel vision.</strong> Adopt other metrics such as biodiversity, soil health, and social dimension.</p><p>ğŸ” <strong>Decentralized creation, approval, and issuance of eco credits.</strong> The process must be viable for smallholder farmers.</p><p>ğŸ¤ <strong>Co-created with communities.</strong> Communities must have a say in creating the regenerative system and be involved in the governance.</p><p>The Conclusion? --&gt; Traditional climate finance is broken. Web3 has the potential to fundamentally transform the accountability, ownership models, and governance of environmental assets. </p><h3 id=\"on-the-ground-%F0%9F%8F%83%E2%80%8D%E2%99%80%EF%B8%8F\">On the ground! ğŸƒâ€â™€ï¸</h3><p>So who from ReFi is out there making the case on the ground ? Here are some of the cool things that were happening this week.</p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/HBAR_foundation\"><strong>HBAR Foundation</strong></a> hosted a ReFi side event. Bringing leading projects such as Filecoin Green and Flowcarbon closer to the policymakers</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">1/2 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Hedera?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Hedera</a> is proud to be hosting the Regenerative Finance <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> event at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/COP27?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#COP27</a> this year with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hubculture?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@hubculture</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/filecoingreen?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@filecoingreen</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TymlezBV?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TymlezBV</a>, Tamuwa, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/weareflowcarbon?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@weareflowcarbon</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/krypctalk?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@krypctalk</a>, and @EveryCity at the Park Regency Resort in Sharm El-Sheikh. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HBAR_foundation?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@HBAR_Foundation</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HubCulture?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HubCulture</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/9k4gS49b4F\">pic.twitter.com/9k4gS49b4F</a></p>&mdash; Hedera (@hedera) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hedera/status/1587776606722048002?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Climatecoin\"><strong>Climate Coin</strong></a> talks about how crypto can play a role in the blue carbon market.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ğŸ“… <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/COP27?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#COP27</a>  - <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Savethedate?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Savethedate</a> ğŸ‘‡<br>Event time 11th November; 9:30 -11:00 am CET<br>Location: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CARICOMorg?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CARICOMorg</a> Pavillion<br><br>A <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Caribbean?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Caribbean</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/BlueCarbon?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#BlueCarbon</a> Market: Exploring Digital Crypto Currency.<br><br>ğŸ‘‡ğŸ§µ <a href=\"https://t.co/O7CyS4AAzH\">pic.twitter.com/O7CyS4AAzH</a></p>&mdash; CLIMATECOINâ„¢ğŸ“COP27 (@Climatecoin) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Climatecoin/status/1589692066556448769?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 7, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ClimateChain\"><strong>Climate Chain Coalition</strong></a> (a UN co-lead initiative) held several sessions on the real world application of ReFi.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Great to see â¦<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CEO_Aniseed?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CEO_Aniseed</a>â© present â¦<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AniseedNFT?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@AniseedNFT</a>â© to the â¦<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ClimateChain?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ClimateChain</a>â© Coalition here at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/cop27?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#cop27</a>! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/refi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#refi</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/cop27egypt?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#cop27egypt</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/rRZkZwxfTR\">pic.twitter.com/rRZkZwxfTR</a></p>&mdash; Wes Geisenberger (@geisenbergerwes) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/geisenbergerwes/status/1589622675206438912?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 7, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>We are only at the 1st week of COP and already so many things are happening. To keep up to date with ReFI at COP27, follow the list from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RKollegala\">@RKollegala</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/lists/1588458798078824448\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/11/image-5.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1198\" height=\"452\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/image-5.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/image-5.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/11/image-5.png 1198w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><h3 id=\"leading-the-way-%F0%9F%9A%80\">Leading the way! ğŸš€</h3><p>With the case for blockchain and Web3 for climate becoming clearer, what countries and jurisdictions are leading the way in implementation? </p><p>ğŸ‡ªğŸ‡¬ <a href=\"https://www.undp.org/egypt/blog/blockchain-climate-action-investing-egypts-farmers-build-low-carbon-future-we-want\">Egypt</a>: As the host of this year's COP, Egypt is paving the way for climate innovation. UNDP lab in Egypt is working with SEKEM and Zero Fund to drive the Egypt 2030 vision powered by blockchain infrastructure. </p><p>ğŸ‡®ğŸ‡© Â <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2022/10/31/indonesia-weighs-a-blockchain-powered-carbon-exchange/\">Indonesia</a>: The Indonesian stock exchange (IDX) is working with a Singaporean startup called MVGX to create a carbon registry and exchange on top of Ethereum.</p><p>ğŸ‡ªğŸ‡º <a href=\"https://www.ledgerinsights.com/blockchain-based-climatetrade-admitted-to-eex-mandatory-carbon-market/\">EU</a>: Blockchain-based ClimateTrade admitted to European (EEX) mandatory carbon market.</p><p>Regardless of latitude or longitude, we need all need to come together, put aside our differences, and work fast on saving the planet and building a better future. Lets make it happen! ğŸ™</p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/U24KODxubVI?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"ReFi Podcast S2E15: Ocean Metagenomics with Courtney and Gordon from New Atlantis DAO\"></iframe></figure><h2 id=\"ocean-metagenomics-with-new-atlantis-dao-%F0%9F%90%A0\">Ocean Metagenomics with New Atlantis DAO ğŸ </h2><p>If Atlantis were a DAO instead of a mythical civilization, it might have been an open platform to regenerate the ocean. That is precisely what New Atlantis DAO is building. </p><p>On this weekâ€™s episode of the ReFi Podcast, hosts johnx25bd and jE talk about Â <a href=\"https://www.scq.ubc.ca/metagenomics-the-science-of-biological-diversity/\">metagenomics</a> for environmental biodiversity with <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/courtnolanad\">Courtney</a> and Gordon from <a href=\"https://newatlantis.io/\">New Atlantis DAO</a>. They want to provide Marine Protected Areas (MPAs) a viable business model by launching a data analytics platform to generate blue carbon and biodiversity credits.</p><p>Check the pod on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC779ZMumuKc6-VMkku1tmyQ/videos\">youtube</a> or any <a href=\"https://podfollow.com/refi-podcast/episode/ebccf254520556fffefbbba258c2a1c4507633a7/view\">podcast app</a> of your choice. And read the written summary deep dive here!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://podfollow.com/refi-podcast/episode/ebccf254520556fffefbbba258c2a1c4507633a7/view\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">ReFi Podcast: Ocean Metagenomics with Courtney and Gordon from New Atlantis DAO</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">John Ellison and Johnx25bd are joined by Courtney and Gordon for an insightful, exciting and deepening conversation about New Atlantis DAO. The two successful entrepreneurs have founded New Atlanti...</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://podfollow.com/assets/icons/android-icon-192x192.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">podfollow</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://podfollow.com/1609683147/episode/ebccf254520556fffefbbba258c2a1c4507633a7/social?v&#x3D;5&amp;pcv&#x3D;1\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-%F0%9F%90%A6\">ReFi ğŸ¦</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"the-latest-across-refi-twitter-and-beyond\">The latest across ReFi Twitter and beyond...</h3></div><h3 id=\"the-hottest-projects-in-the-refi-space-%F0%9F%94%A5\">The hottest projects in the ReFi space ğŸ”¥</h3><p>Just a year after ReFi was born, various projects are popping up and investments are pouring into the space. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PeterOlivier\">Peter Olivier</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/undocarbon\">Undocarbon</a>, recently shared his thought on which projects to support if he were to manage a climate fund.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">who did I forget?<br><br>also, companies that are worthy but a bit too big or late for my pretend checks, and one can never be too cautious with pretend money: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@regen_network</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/weareflowcarbon?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@weareflowcarbon</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ToucanProtocol</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/filecoingreen?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@filecoingreen</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gitcoin</a></p>&mdash; Peter Olivier (@PeterOlivier) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PeterOlivier/status/1588233302070231042?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 3, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"shamba-chainlink-for-smallholder-farmers\">Shamba + Chainlink for Smallholder Farmers</h3><p>Our friends at Shamba have integrated with Chainlink to provide data streams that enable parametric insurance for smallholder farmers. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Weâ€™re excited to announce that Shamba has integrated <a href=\"https://twitter.com/chainlink?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@chainlink</a>&#39;s oracle technology on Arbitrum, Avalanche, Ethereum, Optimism, and Polygon chains to power parametric insurance for smallholder farmers in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Africa?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Africa</a>. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Chainlink?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Chainlink</a><a href=\"https://t.co/t3EMeRJTEX\">https://t.co/t3EMeRJTEX</a></p>&mdash; Shamba (@shambanetwork) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/shambanetwork/status/1590363915787309056?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 9, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"solarpunk-human-maximalism-terrapunk-%F0%9F%A7%91%F0%9F%8F%BF%E2%80%8D%F0%9F%A4%9D%E2%80%8D%F0%9F%A7%91%F0%9F%8F%BB\">Solarpunk + Human maximalism = Terrapunk? ğŸ§‘ğŸ¿â€ğŸ¤â€ğŸ§‘ğŸ» </h3><p>Can we be pro-sustainability &amp; pr0-human at the same time? check out the latest Greenpill podcast on <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/terrapunk\">Terrapunk</a> with <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/nasjaq__\">@nasjaq</a>. A wonderful idea that is optimistic about not just the planet, but also the humanity within it. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ğŸŸ¢GREENPILLğŸŸ¢<br><br>What kind of &#39;punk&#39; best maps to the Ethereum ecosystem?<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nasjaq__?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@nasjaq__</a> is author of the â€˜Terrapunk Manifesto,â€™ which explores Solarpunk from a human-centric perspective<br><br>How can we reconcile being pro-sustainability &amp; pro-human?<br><br>Full show ğŸ‘‡ğŸ‘‡<a href=\"https://t.co/rpKNGYTpar\">https://t.co/rpKNGYTpar</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/sXUpIOrCX7\">pic.twitter.com/sXUpIOrCX7</a></p>&mdash; Bankless (@BanklessHQ) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BanklessHQ/status/1590361765837053952?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 9, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"indigenous-women-fighting-for-the-climate-%E2%9C%8A%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Indigenous women fighting for the climate âœŠğŸ½</h3><p>Each indigenous community is unique, but all of them are facing the same problem. Their way of life is facing a multitude of intertwined challenges. Â Learn about the stories of 6 indigenous women leading the movement to fight climate injustice.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Indigenous women live on the front lines of climate change. They are also leaders in the climate movement.<br><br>This is why we&#39;re joining <a href=\"https://twitter.com/LandRightsNow?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@landrightsnow</a>&#39;s campaign <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SheShouldMaketheNews?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#SheShouldMaketheNews</a>, to tell the stories of indigenous women advancing <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/climatejustice?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#climatejustice</a>.<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/COP27?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#COP27</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/i8mrj57MrG\">pic.twitter.com/i8mrj57MrG</a></p>&mdash; Food Nature Climate (@FNCDialogue) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FNCDialogue/status/1590263378043457541?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 9, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"some-people-are-in-crypto-for-the-greed-but-we-stayed-for-the-hope-%F0%9F%9F%A2\">Some people are in crypto for the greed, but we stayed for the hope ğŸŸ¢</h3><p>We know that it's a tough time for the crypto ecosystem right now. But ReFi is not just about being regenerative but also resilient. We are still very early. Bad days, weeks, and months are nothing if we are working on long term goals such as the 2050 Paris agreement. </p><p> Here are some tweets to keep us optimistic to build a better world with cryptoeconomics.</p><ul><li>Regardless of the market, Rene Reinsberg of Celo is lasered focused on his mission.</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Just want to take a moment to acknowledge everything that&#39;s happening in the industry and reiterate our commitment to the Celo mission. <a href=\"https://t.co/EIDCzqDhhN\">https://t.co/EIDCzqDhhN</a></p>&mdash; Rene Reinsberg (@RegenRene) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RegenRene/status/1590456861609758720?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 9, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><ul><li>Kolektivo showing progress on regeneration, instead of degen doomsday tweets.</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Let&#39;s cleanse those timelines! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> ğŸƒ<br><br>With the past 24 hours&#39; happenings, the future of Web 3.0 may seem bleak. But don&#39;t be fooled; we&#39;re closer than ever to building bottoms-up <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ecosystems?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ecosystems</a> that change the world for good and uplift local communities.<br> <a href=\"https://t.co/fRxqdO6Uc5\">https://t.co/fRxqdO6Uc5</a></p>&mdash; Kolektivo (@Kolektivo) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Kolektivo/status/1590317826320932864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 9, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><ul><li>Jamie Burke of outlier ventures reminding us why ReFi is a non-skeumporphic model of the current financial system.</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We need to stop replicating the excesses of Wall Street and start focusing on building sustainable economic systems. <br><br>The whole FTX saga just further reinforces a push for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> in â€˜23, one that we are already seeing emerge at the early stage venture.</p>&mdash; Jamie Burke â›ºï¸ (@jamie247) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jamie247/status/1590258022663999488?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 9, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Let's show our support to the whole crypto community. ReFi is a non-zero sum game. More love, more impact!</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-events-%F0%9F%AA%A9\">ReFi Events ğŸª©</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"get-your-refi-on-with-friends-in-person-and-online\">Get your ReFi on with friends in-person and online...</h3><a hr